The rules restricting the funding of European football clubs will not interfere with Neymar’s record transfer from Barcelona to Paris-Saint Germain in France.
Any penalties for Paris Saint-Germain will be implemented by EUFA, which oversees European football teams and has the authority to ban teams from participating in the prestigious Champions League.
