Earlier this year, Audi became involved in a criminal investigation of German police into Volkswagen after authorities accused Audi of installing a system that was supposed to circumvent European emissions limits - and thus widened the accusations Audi faces in the US.
The inclusion of Audi in the investigation could have a detrimental impact on Volkswagen: the luxury car makers make up a disproportionate share of Volkswagen’s profits.
